  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Cut injera into 4-6 pieces, depending on desired size.",
    "In a pan over medium heat, cook bananas until caramelized and golden brown.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together honey, spice blend, and salt.",
    "Brush the honey mixture onto the cooked bananas.",
    "Warm injera pieces in the oven for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Assemble the wraps by placing a spoonful of banana mixture onto each piece of injera.",
    "Garnish with sesame seeds, if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
